    "is_free": false,
    "description": "你是悉尼一家水底咖啡馆的老板。你必须为顾客提供美味的咖啡和小吃，让他们满意。游戏的目标是保持商店的顺利和有效运行，同时也让顾客满意。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/04033010c49a5f920687a4efe098edde.poster.avif?t=1753203753\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/04033010c49a5f920687a4efe098edde.webm?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/04033010c49a5f920687a4efe098edde.mp4?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你将有各种任务要做，包括冲泡咖啡，提供食物和饮料，清理店铺等等。你将需要在处理所有这些任务的同时，还要处理不合作的顾客，情绪过山车，你需要脚步敏捷，以保持商店的顺利运行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/a12af607f3f509c60ab31f94e156fb2d.poster.avif?t=1753203753\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/a12af607f3f509c60ab31f94e156fb2d.webm?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/a12af607f3f509c60ab31f94e156fb2d.mp4?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>想象一下......你是这里的老板! 感觉自己是真正的<strong>咖啡馆老板</strong>，一个<strong>帝国的建立者</strong>，并创造整个战略，其中包括。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>装修<br></li><li>雇用和管理员工<br></li><li>照顾供应链<br></li><li>分析预算<br></li><li>为你的咖啡店做广告<br></li><li>还有，最重要的是，让你的顾客满意。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/acaef984f619b51b521b2c19cc375bea.poster.avif?t=1753203753\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/acaef984f619b51b521b2c19cc375bea.webm?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/acaef984f619b51b521b2c19cc375bea.mp4?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你有自己喜欢的咖啡，对吗？你的顾客也一样。做市场调查，找出他们的喜好？使用3D咖啡编辑器来制作不同的食谱，让他们感到高兴。你可以以一种非常有创意的方式组合多种成分。使用不同的层，和浇头，创造出美丽的拿铁艺术!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/c9ec62180f3b3a323431ba78bf7afd87.poster.avif?t=1753203753\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/c9ec62180f3b3a323431ba78bf7afd87.webm?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1904980/extras/c9ec62180f3b3a323431ba78bf7afd87.mp4?t=1753203753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在水下咖啡店，你可以一边享受咖啡，一边探索深海的奥秘! 让自己沉浸在新的咖啡店模拟器中，这是2022年最好的模拟游戏之一! 我们可能并不客观，但我们真的这么认为!<br><br>你是过山车、比萨饼、星球杀手等游戏的忠实粉丝吗？我们是! 建立城市中最好的咖啡馆。创建、定制和管理咖啡师--所有这些都在新的咖啡店模拟游戏中。成为咖啡大亨，创建整个帝国",
